column16: Allen Craig grounds out softly, shortstop Didi Gregorius to first baseman Alex Rodriguez.
Pablo Sandoval strikes out swinging.  Mike Napoli steals (1) 2nd base.
David Ortiz flies out to right fielder Garrett Jones.
Dustin Pedroia grounds out, third baseman Chase Headley to first baseman Alex Rodriguez.
Brock Holt doubles (1) on a fly ball to right fielder Garrett Jones.   Daniel Nava scores.    Xander Bogaerts scores.    Ryan Hanigan scores.
Ryan Hanigan walks.   Daniel Nava to 3rd.    Xander Bogaerts to 2nd.
Xander Bogaerts singles on a sharp ground ball to second baseman Gregorio Petit, deflected by pitcher Matt Tracy.   Daniel Nava to 2nd.
Red Sox challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Daniel Nava reaches on a throwing error by third baseman Chase Headley.
Allen Craig lines out to center fielder Chris Young.
Pablo Sandoval grounds out softly, shortstop Didi Gregorius to first baseman Alex Rodriguez.
